body:
Okay, I&#039;m not a religious nut, nor do I feel some negative way about this, but If she worships her God Nagakabouros, then why is she captain morganin on an Idol of him? Wouldn&#039;t that upset him?
Would you perch your foot on an Idol of Jesus on the cross?
It&#039;s a question I didn&#039;t think about until after I bought her, &amp; started studying her moves, &amp; a good build for her. Is there something I&#039;m not seeing? If so, please explain. {{champion:420}}
